at anak dan dewasa. Kamar mandi shower ada air panas dan dingin. Ada cafe bernuansa diving. Ada warungnya di resepsionis. Overall cukup nyaman buat menginap.\";s:4:\"time\";i:1513865291;}i:1;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"author_name\";s:15:\"Irfan Kurniawan\";s:10:\"author_url\";s:65:\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109529582959040640382/reviews\";s:8:\"language\";s:2:\"id\";s:17:\"profile_photo_url\";s:122:\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/--THeLNCeaMo/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAADv0/5rriqLhTc18/s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4/photo.jpg\";s:6:\"rating\";i:5;s:25:\"relative_time_description\";s:12:\"3 bulan lalu\";s:4:\"text\";s:190:\"Didalam ada kolam renang anak dan dewasa kedalaman air mencapai 3 meter. Suasana tenang banget ademmmm dengan suara air gemericik di telinga. TOP MARGOTOP pokoknya dijaminnnn super nyamannnn\";s:4:\"time\";i:1509336293;}i:2;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"author_name\";s:22:\"Fitria Legiana Lestari\";s:10:\"author_url\";s:65:\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100507213474895668086/reviews\";s:8:\"language\";s:2:\"id\";s:17:\"profile_photo_url\";s:122:\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/-U1CmcqgLryI/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAA7Y/pobCT-kDBAc/s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3/photo.jpg\";s:6:\"rating\";i:3;s:25:\"relative_time_description\";s:12:\"5 bulan lalu\";s:4:\"text\";s:318:\"Tempatnya lmyn luas. Pilihan kamarnya banyak, cuma ya ga design bangunannya blm modern minimalis sprti model skrg, msh design hotel lama. Ada kolam renangnya juga dibelakang. Yang menginap di hotel ini biasanya para karyawan, tapi ada juga kadang2 keluarga. Harga kamarnya terjangkau. Pemiliknya juga ramah dan baik :)\";s:4:\"time\";i:1503529398;}i:3;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"author_name\";s:12:\"ervy deliana\";s:10:\"author_url\";s:65:\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102232886523683145425/reviews\";s:8:\"language\";s:2:\"id\";s:17:\"profile_photo_url\";s:118:\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/-ib077PiW08g/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAAAWQ/ONX7nzifBWo/s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo/photo.jpg\";s:6:\"rating\";i:4;s:25:\"relative_time_description\";s:12:\"6 bulan lalu\";s:4:\"text\";s:183:\"saya rasa tempat ini lumayan... walau td sebagus hotel..nyaman buat istrahat! ga ad ac.. gpp.. ud dingin juga..tapi sayang.. makananya ga ad pulihan...(maunya..kayak d hotel!! hehehe)\";s:4:\"time\";i:1501373034;}i:4;O:8:\"stdClass\":8:{s:11:\"author_name\";s:9:\"Dewabrata\";s:10:\"author_url\";s:65:\"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106603514699230951205/reviews\";s:8:\"language\";s:2:\"id\";s:17:\"profile_photo_url\";s:118:\"https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-6LzaEm8vOAg/AAAAAAAAAAI/AAAAAAAADD8/Fmhj6eC3cDI/s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo/photo.jpg\";s:6:\"rating\";i:2;s:25:\"relative_time_description\";s:12:\"7 bulan lalu\";s:4:\"text\";s:278:\"Belum bisa kasih review kusabab belum nyoba, tp dah booking 5 rooms 3 nights untuk next month. We\'ll see laah yaaww....basically untuk room should be Clean, smell good, safety dan karyawan yang ramah dan responsive. daah aah itu dulu....see you. (meanwhile dua star dulu ya) :-)\";s:4:\"time\";i:1498194220;}}s:5:\"scope\";s:6:\"GOOGLE\";s:5:\"types\";a:3:{i:0;s:7:\"lodging\";i:1;s:17:\"point_of_interest\";i:2;s:13:\"establishment\";}s:3:\"url\";s:49:\"https://maps.google.com/?cid=13742425952478915120\";s:10:\"utc_offset\";i:420;s:8:\"vicinity\";s:66:\"Jalan Amir Mahmud No. 465, Karangmekar, Cimahi Tengah, Karangmekar\";}s:6:\"status\";s:2:\"OK\";}");
